api - 类 中的变量com.github.wzclouds.injection.core.InjectionFieldPo

api() 和 feign() 任选其一, 使用 api时，请填写实现类， 使用feign时，填写接口即可 如： @InjectionField(api="userServiceImpl") 等价于 @InjectionField(feign=UserService.class) 如： @InjectionField(api="userController") 等价于 @InjectionField(feign=UserApi.class)

InjectionField - com.github.wzclouds.injection.annonation中的注释类型
在某个对象的字段上标记该注解，该字段的值将被主动注入 如： \@InjectionField(api = "dictionaryItemServiceImpl", method = "findDictionaryItem") private String nation; \@InjectionField(api = "dictionaryItemServiceImpl", method = "findDictionaryItem") private RemoteData nation; \@InjectionField(api = "dictionaryApi", method = "findDictionaryItem") private RemoteData nation; \@InjectionField(api = "userApi", method = "findUserByIds", beanClass = User.class) private RemoteData user; 强烈建议：不要对象之间互相依赖 如： User 想要注入 File， File也想注入User
